# Build artifacts
/bin/
/dist/
*.test
*.out
coverage.*

# Editor / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Node (for documentation tooling, e.g., link-check action runs)
node_modules/

# Defense-in-depth: legacy framework version (v1/v2) directories.
# These do not apply to v3's `work/` layout and shouldn't appear here.
# Note: `work/epics/` was originally listed too as a defense-in-depth
# entry against the framework writing to its own tree, but G38 turned
# this repo into a consumer (epics + milestones live under `work/epics/`
# now); that line was removed in the G38 follow-up.
.ai/
.ai-repo/
.github/skills/

# .claude/ is gitignored except the shared project config: the status line
# script and the project-level settings.json. Per-user files stay local.
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/statusline.sh

# Drafts that ship to proliminal.net/notes are written and revised locally,
# not tracked in this repo. They face publicly via proliminal, not via git.
docs/notes/

# Local scratch space — extracted notes, mining outputs, repo-specific
# artifacts pulled from external projects. Sanitize before promoting anything
# from here into tracked docs.
.scratch/

# `aiwf render --format=html` output directory.
site/

# Local-build artifact. Anchored to repo root: only the binary at /aiwf gets
# ignored; the cmd/aiwf source directory must remain trackable.
/aiwf

# aiwf: materialized skill adapters (regenerated by aiwf update)
.claude/skills/.aiwf-owned
.claude/skills/aiwf-*/

# aiwfx-whiteboard: gitignored local cache of the last open-work
# synthesis output (regenerated on each skill invocation; see the
# aiwfx-whiteboard skill body §"Output cache").
WHITEBOARD.md
